div.div: Commented on #662 feat: add filter by column type on repositories screen

@bdougie we can sort the data by name, pr count, pr velocity and spam. Note that they are done inside Repositories organisms (where we have access to the table title). However, I didn't manage to sort them by activity or contribution because those data are fetched using different hooks (by providing the repo id ) inside RepoRow molecule (repositories -> repository-table -> repo-row).
